beer.beer_description:
This Yak uses Melba and Galaxy hops to provide an
enticing tropical fruit aroma, complemented by the
delicate citrus notes of Cascade hops. A combination of pale and wheat malt provide a light palate rounding out the low bitterness. Brewed for GABS 2016
